    "2ab75f39-7f55-452b-b9d7-e513d395c914": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "template--20862860820772__2ab75f39-7f55-452b-b9d7-e513d395c914-block-1": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "1. What is Breathelet?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet is a stylish bracelet that delivers <strong>random, gentle vibrations</strong> as subtle cues to <strong>take a pause and reconnect with yourself</strong>. It’s your wearable companion for mindfulness, calm, and intentional living.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "template--20862860820772__2ab75f39-7f55-452b-b9d7-e513d395c914-block-2": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "2. How does Breathelet work?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet sends tested, random vibrations designed to give the most beneficial reminders. Each vibration encourages you to slow down, reset your focus, and be present in the moment. Over time, these nudges encourage mindfulness and a calmer state of mind.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "template--20862860820772__2ab75f39-7f55-452b-b9d7-e513d395c914-block-3": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "3. Who is Breathelet for?",
            "content": "<p>Anyone looking to live more mindfully, reduce stress, or build positive daily habits. Whether at work, commuting, or at home, Breathelet is there to gently remind you to take a pause.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_bAmgKe": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "4. Can I use it for things other than breathing?",
            "content": "<p> Absolutely! Breathelet can help you:</p><ul><li>Take a mindful breath</li><li>Practice gratitude</li><li>Hydrate</li><li>Share a smile</li><li>Check in with yourself and stay grounded in the moment</li></ul>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_gF4iTE": {
          "type": "block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "5. How should I wear my Breathelet?",
            "content": "<p>For the intended experience, Breathelet should be worn <strong>snug against your wrist — not loose</strong>.</p><p>A loose fit may reduce or completely limit your ability to feel these subtle reminders. A secure, close fit ensures you stay connected to every moment of calm.</p><p><strong>Important:</strong> A loose fit is the #1 reason users don’t feel the vibration properly.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_nk7TGJ": {
          "type": "block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "6. What is the ideal fit?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet should feel:</p><ul><li><strong>Secure and stable</strong> on your wrist </li><li><strong>Comfortably snug</strong>, without restricting movement </li></ul><p>If the bracelet shifts, slides, or hangs away from your wrist, it is too loose.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_yPWnmA": {
          "type": "block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "7. Why am I not feeling the vibration?",
            "content": "<p>This is usually due to the fit. <br/>Make sure that:</p><ul><li> The Breathelet is worn snug on your wrist </li><li> The bracelet is not loose or dangling </li></ul><p>Once properly adjusted, you should feel the gentle vibration clearly.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_pLAmgT": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "5. Is it waterproof?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Both Classic and OneFit- are water-resistant, so they handle everyday splashes, sweat, or rain.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_PMRppU": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "6. Are there any screens or apps?",
            "content": "<p>No screens. No Bluetooth. No distractions. Breathelet is designed to be a simple, elegant wearable that helps you reconnect with your mind and body.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_GJqnQJ": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "7. How can I get support?",
            "content": "<p>For questions, troubleshooting, or replacement strings, contact support@breathelet.com<br/><br/></p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        }
      },
